--- Lokk / Axis ---

Lokk leaps to the side, behind a rock, as McGowan's missile 
smashes into the ground behind him, "Whew..." He reloads his 
weapons then whips both chain guns over the rock to face 
McGowan, and unloads his clips, spraying the groups with fifty 
bullets. He guns start to click indicating ammunition depletion. He 
ducks behind the rock to reload.

Axis covers his face with his arm as a laser beam sears that limb. 
several other lasers streak by him, one smoking him in the knee. 
His charging laser at full power, Axis levels his laser and fires twice 
at Barrymore. His missile launcher follows up with another missile 
heading into the group of bots.
